📝 My Tasks — Todo App

A simple Android Todo app built with Kotlin, MVVM Architecture and Room Database. Built as a learning project to understand modern Android development before my internship.


Features


Add, edit and delete tasks
Data saved locally using Room Database
UI updates automatically with LiveData



Tech Stack


Kotlin
MVVM Architecture
Room Database
LiveData & ViewModel
RecyclerView



Architecture

UI → ViewModel → Repository → Room Database


What I Learned


How MVVM architecture works in a real project
How Room Database stores data locally
How ViewModel survives screen rotation
How LiveData updates the UI automatically



Credits

Built by following the Neat Roots tutorial on YouTube.
